\f0\i\b\fs28 Introduction \
\pard\pardeftab720

\f1\i0\b0\fs24 \cf0 This document describes how to set up the open source Adapt It project for building with Xcode 4.6.3 and Code::Blocks on Mac OS X Mountain Lion (10.8.4). You can download the latest version of Xcode from Apple's website at:\
\
\pard\pardeftab720
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://developer.apple.com/technologies/tools/"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc0 http://developer.apple.com/technologies/tools/}}\
\
The download requires free ADC registration to get your Apple ID and Password. You should download the latest Xcode which will work on your Mac OS X version. We are using Mac Mountain Lion 10.8.4 which can use Xcode 4.6.3.\
\
The open source Adapt It project is hosted by GoogleCode at:\
\
\pard\pardeftab720
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://code.google.com/p/adaptit/"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc0 http://code.google.com/p/adaptit/}}\
\
The earlier versions of these instructions were written after finding the Xcode documentation in the various wxWidgets Wiki articles to be incomplete or misleading. The most recent Wiki articles are at: \
\
\pard\pardeftab720
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wiki.wxwidgets.org/Compiling_wxWidgets_with_Xcode"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc0 http://wiki.wxwidgets.org/Compiling_wxWidgets_with_Xcode}}\
\pard\pardeftab720

\i \cf0 NOTE: This Web page has the status \cf3 Partly Out of Date\cf0  - quite correct since it describes using MacOS X 10.5.6, wxWidgets 2.8.9, and Xcode 3.1.2!
\i0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wiki.wxwidgets.org/Creating_Xcode_projects_for_wxWidgets_applications"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc0 http://wiki.wxwidgets.org/Creating_Xcode_projects_for_wxWidgets_applications}}\
\pard\pardeftab720

\i \cf0 NOTE: This describes using MacOS X 10.7.3, wxWidgets 2.9.x, and Xcode 4.3.2
\i0 \
\
and\
\
\pard\pardeftab720
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wiki.wxwidgets.org/Development:_wxMac#Building_under_10.6_Snow_Leopard"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc0 http://wiki.wxwidgets.org/Development:_wxMac#Building_under_10.6_Snow_Leopard}}\
\pard\pardeftab720

